latestPosts.caption:
Starting skincare? Don’t make these 4 common mistakes!👇
1️⃣ Using too many products — it can confuse and irritate your skin.
2️⃣ Scrubbing your face daily — over-exfoliation leads to dryness and sensitivity.
3️⃣ Jumping into retinol or acids without guidance — always consult a dermatologist before using strong actives.
4️⃣ Skipping sunscreen — no matter what you apply, UV rays will still do their damage!

Your skin doesn’t need to be perfect — it just needs to be healthy. 💗

Save this for later & comment “routine” if you want a BEGINNER -FRIENDLY one I personally trust!
Love, Chahat 🫰🏻
